====== Floe: Command pipe for web publishing ======

The aim of Floe is to build web applications using the principles of [[http://todotxt.org|todo.txt]]

==== What does Floe do? ====


  * Merges Django, Rails, and PHP5 web projects
  * Provides a task based environment for scripting development tools
  * Provides a PHP5 architecture for simple web applications
  * Mashes PHP5, Ruby, and Python (and probably Perl soon)

